day,  is  based  on  models  and  assumptions,  rather  than  facts,  and 
we’ll need some time to see if it will play out. 

Finally,  there  are  uncertainties  around  Deepwater  funding. 
When  the  program  began,  we  expressed  the  concern  that  this  pro-
