Coast  Guard’s  revised  Deepwater  Implementation  Plan.  My  testimony  will  focus  on 
the following: 

vised implementation plan; 

National Security Cutters (NSCs) and Offshore Patrol Cutters (OPCs); 

• the  level  of  overall  mission  performance  that  would  be  achieved  under  the  re-
• the  option  of  accelerating  and  possibly  expanding  procurement  of  Deepwater 
• the  relationship  between  Deepwater  cutters  and  the  Navy’s  planned  Littoral 
• the  timeliness  of  delivery  to  Congress  of  detailed  Deepwater  cost  and  schedule 
