DiMascio,  ‘‘Army  Announces  Future  Combat  System  Contract  Restructuring,’’  Inside  the  Army, 
April 11, 2005; and Jonathan Karp and Andy Pasztor, ‘‘About-Face: Army’s Decision On Boeing 
Changes Philosophy,’’ Wall Street Journal, April 6, 2005. 

